query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 chn ci n mk) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 chn ci k mk n t kt) */ select min(t.title) AS complete_downey_ironman_movie
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%Sisters,%'
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind like '%complete%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name not like '%Sherlock%' AND chn.name like '%Three%'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('gore',
'marvel-comics',
'death',
'sequel',
'fight',
'tv-special',
'revenge',
'1001-nights')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1957
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie';
